    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275010/extras/c55453b28e2d658ede8adb7e0c043dfb.poster.avif?t=1749576187\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275010/extras/c55453b28e2d658ede8adb7e0c043dfb.webm?t=1749576187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>增强自己，小心诅咒！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每选择一个增益效果，循环就会变强，并迫使你选择一个诅咒。你的成功取决于做出增强力量的策略性决策，同时应对循环带来的更多挑战，最终引领你走向胜利！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275010/extras/9094fe3b48dadbf3dda651e28b93ee26.poster.avif?t=1749576187\" width=600 height=337 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275010/extras/9094fe3b48dadbf3dda651e28b93ee26.webm?t=1749576187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>逐个击败首领，突破循环！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败守护每个循环出口的强大首领，解锁新的路径，逐步迈向自由。每一次胜利都让你离打破无尽循环更近一步！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275010/extras/ab762aa934d70301ae6fb22bc2d0413a.poster.avif?t=1749576187\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275010/extras/ab762aa934d70301ae6fb22bc2d0413a.webm?t=1749576187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>接受失败，变得更强！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次失败的逃脱都会让你变得更强，为你的旅程提供宝贵的经验。拥抱挑战，从错误中汲取教训，重新尝试，但这次你将带着更强的策略和新获得的韧性，克服面前的障碍</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275010/extras/cfc012c67b014676eb07da3e60f103d2.poster.avif?t=1749576187\" width=600 height=337 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275010/extras/cfc012c67b014676eb07da3e60f103d2.webm?t=1749576187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >创造强大的协同效果！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >结合多种技能和遗物，创造各种强大的协同效果，每一种都能在你逃脱循环的冒险中提供独特的优势！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275010/extras/50ff1cc1de1ab51c7186a416b6b46098.poster.avif?t=1749576187\" width=600 height=337 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275010/extras/50ff1cc1de1ab51c7186a416b6b46098.webm?t=1749576187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
